{"tid":2196956,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"趙立堅: 美國政府公然採取損害中國在美留學人員合法權益的措施，是赤裸裸的政治迫害和種族歧視","createTime":"2020-09-10T09:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T09:51:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"24a5e757ac2e3d9b950917e01e903b8a1257d56f","tid":2196956,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"美國至今撤銷過千名中國公民的簽證，阻止被認為對美國國家安全存在風險的學生及研究人員入境。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅表示，美國政府公然採取損害中國在美留學人員合法權益的措施，是赤裸裸的政治迫害和種族歧視，嚴重侵犯中國留學生的人權，美方應立即停止利用各種藉口，對在美中國留學人員的無端限制和打壓，中方支持中國留學人員依法維護他們合法正當權益，中方保留對此事作出進一步反應的權利。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅又說，一段時間以來，美方在中美人文交流領域，採取一系列消極言行，對中美正常人員交流和人員往來帶來嚴重消極影響，嚴重損害兩國關係社會基礎。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548892-20200910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548892-20200910.htm&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2SJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=20864d7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548892-20200910.htm&h=5d1fde9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548892-20200910.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e04d35d457f9e873aa719c2bc26c39ef7d2eff81","tid":2196956,"uid":39777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"干預內政？"},{"pid":"0d2ff108897dd674e359ab291e38678dfef78133","tid":2196956,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"口交冇用架<br />\n反制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a010b9e3133ce70105d32f0dce3279146c69ccd","tid":2196956,"uid":295477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c5293c9db89c5bb711b42610d53c35f3b1b1f8","tid":2196956,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc